milestones.description: Aasif Karim has become the top wicket-taker for KENYA in ODIs with 13 wickets, going past Rajab Ali's 11
This is the lowest match aggregate (202) involving teams Bangladesh & Kenya in ODIs
Chudasama has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (12) for KENYA, going past Aasif Karim
